U.K. Lawmakers to Publish Phone Hacking Report July 20, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-19T21:52:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/u-k-lawmakers-to-publish-phone-hacking-report-july-20-sky-says.html
U.K. lawmakers’ Home Affairs
Committee will publish a report into the phone hacking scandal
tomorrow morning, committee Chairman Keith Vaz told Sky News in
an interview. The committee “thoroughly examined all the
issues,” Vaz told Sky.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
